{"tid":399410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有一日 你突然穿越左翻去古代 你會點選擇?","createTime":"2017-09-14T02:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T03:07:34.000Z","uid":137768,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9471896f6eacee2b0ed4ff3357bf4815cb6fa340","tid":399410,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"你翻到去嘅古代 係一個戰火連天嘅時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔清楚呢度係咩地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  亦都唔識講佢地嘅語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n受戰亂影響 所有平民都家破人亡 到處逃亡 糧食不足<br />\n去到要食樹皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  易子而食嘅地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n罪案更係到處發生 有咁亂得咁亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而為左生存嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n會帶邊五樣(3個下面揀＋2樣自選)野翻去呢？<br />\n<br />\n揀三樣:<br />\n1)槍械 (彈藥有限)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2)乾糧 (任選帶幾多 但要拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n3)食水 (同上)<br />\n4)手機電腦 (可以用單機程式 但無得cha電)<br />\n5)西史書<br />\n6)金銀珠寶<br />\n7)冷武器 e.g.(軍刀)<br />\n8)一眾兄弟/姊妹 朋友 (拖晒大家落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n9)急救藥箱 <br />\n10)某方面嘅專家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n11)家人 (條女/條仔都計)<br />\n12)衣服裝備 (e.g. 行山嗰啲)<br />\n<br />\n加自選兩樣:<br />\n13) 自選<br />\n14) 自選<br />\n<br />\n記住目標係生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  歡迎選擇討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s. 最好覆時寫埋樣野係咩 唔係得no.好難討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae66d37ec26ba2a123ab4b37bbb5983fa47f654","tid":399410,"uid":59192,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n樓主女朋友<br />\n樓主老母"},{"pid":"152512880077d3ceaa3ddca2fede2d076e2798f3","tid":399410,"uid":128600,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"員工証"},{"pid":"8645da64f19f2b5b3605d9ee51d4971f1056f829","tid":399410,"uid":4709,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"必選：<br />\n刀<br />\n水<br />\n港督<br />\n<br />\n自選：<br />\n豆豉鯪魚<br />\n避孕袋"},{"pid":"1bec2b9fc8ccb4f2bf14bc7f5d7e5db3769cb70c","tid":399410,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n我會揀:<br />\n水<br />\n食物<br />\n槍<br />\n太陽能車 (搏佢唔落雨同儲電夜晚夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n美國士兵 (應該可以做保標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n只係逃亡應該唔至於會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40718cfde38a1d01f84ececf9329b28ebb27e4b2","tid":399410,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主<br />\n樓主女朋友<br />\n樓主老母</blockquote><br />\n認真po黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f3c333d3ec5b89e4f8c890043183030d9207a8","tid":399410,"uid":52369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"槍 手提電腦 食物 太陽能電擊棒 太陽能充電器"},{"pid":"eb6e9d19643e465b1bc1a572a99e89fd6c0fbc4d","tid":399410,"uid":143543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"你冇睇No game no life 架咩? 去異世界要帶手機同太陽能叉電器架"},{"pid":"2a4f06292b09ede64903c860f34ff65bf47bdb86","tid":399410,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"一個水壺一把刀就夠<br />\n利申:工程師"},{"pid":"47fd5d4edc7dbc4fc990d841d96b30b92198bd93","tid":399410,"