sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n3)食水 (同上)<br />\n4)手機電腦 (可以用單機程式 但無得cha電)<br />\n5)西史書<br />\n6)金銀珠寶<br />\n7)冷武器 e.g.(軍刀)<br />\n8)一眾兄弟/姊妹 朋友 (拖晒大家落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n9)急救藥箱 <br />\n10)某方面嘅專家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n11)家人 (條女/條仔都計)<br />\n12)衣服裝備 (e.g. 行山嗰啲)<br />\n<br />\n加自選兩樣:<br />\n13) 自選<br />\n14) 自選<br />\n<br />\n記住目標係生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  歡迎選擇討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s. 最好覆時寫埋樣野係咩 唔係得no.好難討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乾糧<br />\n食水<br />\n野外求生專家<br />\n<br />\n核彈<br />\n抗生素</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n核彈發射唔到，fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有倒數計時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界既神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3342a03fec42f56c8e3aa7c3da341e04797f38d","tid":399410,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"等等<br />\n如果我有個專家黎，<br />\n個專家有無得又自選？<br />\n然後無限loop帶專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea04a14091cd92e4991c1616cb63b11fbd507aa6","tid":399410,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.西史書<br />\n2.金銀珠寶<br />\n3.古語言學專家<br />\n<br />\n自選：<br />\n1.中史書<br />\n2.一對柴犬<br />\n<br />\n可以建立新國家or扶搖本來國家再奪權<br />\n或者做下神棍扮預言家<br />\n柴犬係解悶之用</blockquote><br />\n書有咩用，你一打算投身官場/謀反，世界已經唔會按住書咁發展，除非你一直做平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ea706787ee4ecbadf36c0cde0e3a90124a36ea","tid":399410,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>槍 手提電腦 食物 太陽能電擊棒 太陽能充電器